simplyblock-proxmox (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bump API version
  * Suppress nvme-cli output
  * Connect devices on demand
  * Allow configuration of connection parameters
  * Extend local device lookup
  * Add use of keep-alive-timeout
  * Repair failed device connections
  * Document connection semantics
  * Enable full clones of volumes
  * Internally prefix snapshots with volume name
  * Enable CoW image clones
  * Allow marking storage as shared
  * Enable template storage
  * Ensure changed plugin is loaded

